{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id44c62418-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1243"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1243"},"text":"§ 1243.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Loss of small business investment company","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In the case of a small business investment company operating under the Small Business Investment Act of 1958, if—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id44c62419-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1243/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a loss is on stock received pursuant to the conversion privilege of convertible debentures acquired pursuant to section 304 of the Small Business Investment Act of 1958, and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id44c6241a-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1243/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" such loss would (but for this section) be a loss from the sale or exchange of a capital asset,","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n\n"},{"tag":"continuation","attrib":{},"text":"then such loss shall be treated as an ordinary loss.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id44c6241b-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/85/866/tI/s57/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 85–866, title I, § 57(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1958-09-02"},"text":"Sept. 2, 1958","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/72/1645"},"text":"72 Stat. 1645","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/172/tIV/s433/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 91–172, title IV, § 433(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1969-12-30"},"text":"Dec. 30, 1969","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/83/624"},"text":"83 Stat. 624","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/455/tXIX/s1901/b/3/F"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–455, title XIX, § 1901(b)(3)(F)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-10-04"},"text":"Oct. 4, 1976","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/90/1793"},"text":"90 Stat. 1793","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id44c6241c-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id44c6241d-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id44c6241e-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Small Business Investment Act of 1958, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/85/699"},"text":"Pub. L. 85–699","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1958-08-21"},"text":"Aug. 21, 1958","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/72/689"},"text":"72 Stat. 689","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to chapter 14B (§ 661 et seq.) of Title 15, Commerce and Trade. Section 304 of the Small Business Investment Act of 1958, is classified to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s684"},"text":"section 684 of Title 15","children":[],"tail":". For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s661"},"text":"section 661 of Title 15","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id44c6241f-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1976—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/455"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–455","children":[],"tail":" substituted “an ordinary loss” for “a loss from the sale or exchange of property which is not a capital asset”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1969—Par. (1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/172"},"text":"Pub. L. 91–172","children":[],"tail":" substituted “stock received pursuant to the conversion privilege of convertible debentures” for “convertible debentures (including stock received pursuant to the conversion privilege)”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id44c62420-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id44c62421-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 1976 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/455"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–455","children":[],"tail":" applicable with respect to taxable years beginning after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-12-31"},"text":"Dec. 31, 1976","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/455/s1901/d"},"text":"section 1901(d) of Pub. L. 94–455","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/